> windlord typed some buttons hopping to scan the signature of the predacons

IFF signatures were difficult to pick up at first as it seemed that
they were far underground. But finally the computer came back with
BLIGHT and POWERPINCH, they appeared to be going towards one of the
older lava shafts far underneath the ground.

BLIGHT = http://tfwiki.net/wiki/Scourge_%28BW%29
POWERPINCH = http://tfwiki.net/wiki/Powerpinch

Meanwhile there were other proto humans milling around above the
ground near the top of the volcano, there were standing before a
statue of some sort. These look far less apelike than most that have
been seen

The Proto humans appeared to be unaware of the PREDACONS who were far
underneath them.
